ics)|Jumbo Elliott]]\n| [[Track and field athletics|Track and field]]\n| Local, [[Villanova Wildcats|Villanova University]]\n|-\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|[[Edward Gottlieb|Eddie Gottlieb]]\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|Basketball\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|Local, [[Philadelphia Sphas|SPHAS]], Philadelphia Warriors, Philadelphia Stars\n|-\n| [[Lefty Grove]]\n| Baseball\n| Philadelphia Athletics\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Carl Lewis]]\n||Track and Field\n||Local; [[Willingboro High School|Willingboro High]]\n|-\n| [[Robert P. Levy|Bob Levy]]\n| Lifetime Commitment\n| Contributor, Youth Sports, University of Pennsylvania\n|-\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|[[Tommy McDonald (American football)|Tommy McDonald]]\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|Football\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|Philadelphia Eagles\n|-\n| [[Pete Pihos]]\n| Football\n| Philadelphia Eagles\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Harvey Pollack]]\n||Legacy of Excellence\n||Stat-Man Extraodinaire\n|-\n| [[Guy Rodgers]]\n| Basketball\n| Local, Temple University, Philadelphia Warriors\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Cathy Rush]]\n||Basketball\n||Local, [[Immaculata College]]\n|-\n| [[Vic Seixas]]\n| Tennis\n| Local\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Jay Sigel]]\n||[[Golf]]\n||Local\n|-\n| [[Ed Snider]]\n| Philadelphia Medal\n| Owner, Sports/Entertainment Industry Leader\n|-\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|[[Joe Verdeur]]\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|[[Swimming (sport)|Swimming]]\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|Local, [[Northeast Catholic High School|Northeast Catholic High]], La Salle University\n|-\n|rowspan=17|2006\n| [[1960 Philadelphia Eagles season|1960 Philadelphia Eagles]]\n| Football\n| [[1960 NFL season|NFL Champions]]\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Herb Adderley]]\n||Football\n||Local\n|-\n| [[Don Bragg]]\n| Track and Field\n| Local, Villanova University\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Roy Campanella]]\n||Baseball\n||Local\n|-\n| [[Ray Didinger]]\n| Legacy of Excellence\n| Local, [[Sportswriter]], Broadcaster\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Bill Ellerbee]]\n||Lifetime Commitment\n||High School Basketball Coach, Teacher, Mentor\n|-\n| [[Del Ennis]]\n| Baseball\n| Local, Philadelphia Phillies\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Joe Fulks]]\n||Basketball\n||Philadelphia Warriors\n|-\n| [[Hal Greer]]\n| Basketball\n| Philadelphia 76ers\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Gene Hart]]\n||Legacy of Excellence\n||Philadelphia Flyers Broadcaster\n|-\n| [[Reggie Jackson]]\n| Baseball\n| Local\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Willie Mosconi]]\n||[[Billiards]]\n||Local\n|-\n| [[The Palestra]]\n| Venue Enshrinement\n| Basketball\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Jack Ramsay]]\n||Basketball\n||Local, [[Saint Joseph's Hawks men's basketball|Saint Joseph's University]], Philadelphia 76ers\n|-\n| [[Al Simmons]]\n| Baseball\n| Philadelphia Athletics\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Anne Townsend]]\n||[[Field Hockey]]\n||Local\n|-\n| [[Helen Sigel Wilson]]\n| Golf\n| Local\n|-\n|rowspan=14|2007\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|[[1980 Philadelphia Phillies season|1980 Philadelphia Phillies]]\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|Baseball\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|[[1980 World Series|World Series Champions]]\n|-\n| [[Beth Anders]]\n| Field Hockey\n| Local\n|-\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|[[Walter Bahr]]\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|[[Association football|Soccer]]\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|Local\n|-\n| [[Bill Barber]]\n| Hockey\n| Philadelphia Flyers\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Mickey Cochrane]]\n||Baseball\n||Philadelphia Athletics\n|-\n| [[Chuck Klein]]\n| Baseball\n| Philadelphia Phillies\n|-\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|[[Bill Lyon (sportswriter)|Bill Lyon]]\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|Legacy of Excellence\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|Sportswriter, ''[[Philadelphia Inquirer]]'', Author\n|-\n| [[Theresa Grentz]]\n| Basketball\n| Local, Immaculata College\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Frank Kilroy]]\n||Football\n||Local, [[Temple Owls football|Temple University]], Philadelphia Eagles\n|-\n| [[Harry Litwack]]\n| Basketball\n| Local, Temple University\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Earl Monroe]]\n||Basketball\n||Local\n|-\n| [[Greasy Neale]]\n| Football\n| Philadelphia Eagles\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Jack Whitaker]]\n||Legacy of Excellence\n||Local, [[Saint Joseph's University]], Sportscaster\n|-\n| [[Reggie White]]\n| Football\n| Philadelphia Eagles\n|-\n|rowspan=14|2008\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|[[1929 Philadelphia Athletics season|1929 Philadelphia Athletics]]\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|Baseball\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|World Series Champion\n|-\n| [[Leroy Burrell]]\n| Track and Field\n| Local\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Harold Carmichael]]\n||Football\n||Philadelphia Eagles\n|-\n| [[Maurice Cheeks]]\n| Basketball\n| Philadelphia 76ers\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Ed Delahanty]]\n||Baseball\n||Philadelphia Phillies\n|-\n| [[Stan Hochman]]\n| Legacy of Excellence\n| Sportswriter, ''[[Philadelphia Daily News]]''\n|-\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|[[Charles Jenkins Sr.|Charles Jenkins]]\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|Track and Field\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|\n|-\n| [[Tommy Loughran]]\n| Boxing\n| Local\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Herb Magee]]\n||Basketball\n||Local, [[Philadelphia University]]\n|-\n| [[Dorothy Germain Porter]]\n| Golf\n| Local\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Fred Shero]]\n||Hockey\n||Philadelphia Flyers\n|-\n| [[Lionel Simmons]]\n| Basketball\n| Local, La Salle University\n|- style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"\n||[[Mickey Vernon]]\n||Baseball\n||Local\n|-\n| [[Al Wistert]]\n| Football\n| Philadelphia Eagles\n|-\n|rowspan=14|2009\n| style=\"background:#ffe6bd;\"|[[1973\u201374 Philadelphia Flyers season|1974]] & [[1974\u201375 Philadelphia Flyers season|1975 Philadelphia Flyers]]\n| style=\"backgr